data.description: Beautiful home in a beautiful neighborhood with amazing warm tones throughout. Large 5 bedroom with 2 great living areas, room for the whole family! Great central location to great schools and ease to your shopping favorites! The lots in the neighborhood are a little larger than the other nearby neighborhoods so more space to play and entertain! It also has an amazing mint and butterfly garden on the side! And did I say NO HOA! This gem won’t last long!
